Interestingly, before the black bull NTR trope became popular, the most prevailing trope for NTR hentai features the "Yellow Hair" who is usually a delinquent. He is usually blond haired and tanned, both fashion trends came from western influence to Japan and were often adopted by the middle upper class young adults who wanted to stand out and seem fashionable. The "Yellow Haired Delinquent" embodies the xenophobic view many Japanese people had at the time that westerners are often ill-mannered, lazy, inconsiderate, selfish and dishonest. They had this same fear that these people are unfit for their society and will also "corrupt" women with their despicable and hedonistic ways. And the source of that fear, xenophobia, is a large reason why foreign residents in Japan are more likely to be mistreated. (i.e. refused from purchasing housing, refused service in restaurants, mistreated by the police)
